ow.</p><p><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(41, 90, 238);\"><em>+ Alex hates you. Live with it...</em></span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fgykLEr8FJBmCqYO6bIDI.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(41, 90, 238);\"><strong>LINKS TO OTHER IDIOTS FROM THE GROUP:</strong></span></p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/179cd8e0-b2ef-4adb-a66f-a1d50a4ce3c8_character-ts-alex-fallon\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Alex Fallon</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 204, 204);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 103, 255);\"><strong><em>Hated roommate (u here!)</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 204, 204);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>|</strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e73b50ff-6a74-48f4-b304-fd5ef7d5abc8_character-ts-alex-fallon-alt\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Alex Fallon</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 204, 204);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 103, 255);\"><strong><em>Trip to the festival (ALT)</em></strong></span></a><br><br></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4rN0OdIVQu3IFcMnT-uJM.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c3c89053-b746-405f-b097-f5d750fe6811_character-ts-matthew-gilberd\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Matthew Gilberd </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 94, 156);\"><strong><em>Audition for a band (original)</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 94, 156);\"><strong><em> | </em></strong></span><span 